text: LK Zug is a Swiss women's handball club from Zug. They won four national championships between 2010 and 2016.Club profile in the Swiss Handball Federation They have been a regular in EHF competitions since the 1990s, participating twice to the EHF Champions League. ==Titles== * Swiss Premium League (4) ** 2010, 2013, 2014, 2015 * Swiss Cups (2) ** 2014, 2015 * Swiss Supercup (1) ** 2016 ==European record == {| class="wikitable" !
